        <abstract> 
<p>JDH has confirmed CD’s opinion on the affinities of species in great genera. Is looking at large genera in several local <hi rend="italic">Floras</hi> to find the "range &amp; commonness of varying species".</p> 
            <p>Has been "beyond measure interested" in the construction instincts of the hive-bee.</p>
